description:
&lt;p&gt;NCL CCG (Enfield borough) are looking to recruit an experienced, motivated Registered Nurse – Learning Disabilities with excellent communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Nurse Assessor will co-ordinate and undertake Checklists, FNC assessments and reviews in care homes as per the National Framework for Continuing Healthcare (CHC) and funded Nursing Care (2018).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Nurse Assessor will work closely with social care, palliative care and private providers to ensure that timely, appropriate quality care is provided. Clinical rationale will be required to ensure that resources are optimised and commissioning is clinically based and regularly reviewed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Ann Mount, Clinical Lead on 0203 8163728 for an informal discussion or apply on line&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAnn MountJob titleClinical Lead Continuing Health CareEmail addressannmount@nhs.netTelephone number02038163728&lt;/p&gt;
